<h1>What's new in EVO 3 ?</h1>
<h3>Evolution CMS 3.0 RC3</h3>
<ul>
<li>Update to Laravel 8</li>
<li>Add TVs for Users</li>
<li>evo() short name for evolutionCMS()  ($modx = $evo();)</li>
<li>Now work in BLADE: @auth, <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/guest/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/guest">@guest</a>, <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="organization" data-hovercard-url="/orgs/csrf/hovercard" href="https://github.com/csrf">@csrf</a></li>
